postcontent: This is a special Glock 30 custom.  It has a nickel borron slide and barrel with duracoted flames. It also has a custom stainless steel guide rod and spring.  It will come with glock case and 4 10rd mags with finger extensions, (original mag bottoms included as well) It also has custom night sites added. This is a fantastic conceiled carry piece or range pistol.  The Nickel Borron slide reduces friction and assists for faster and smoother running action along with the custom springs it makes for a very soft shooting 45.  Do some research online google  glock 30 you will find a ton of info about how this particular model is notorious for being one of the softest shooting 45s, and special mojo accuracy.  People cant really explain why but it is way more accurate than comparable pistols.  it has to do with the barrel angle at the time of the bullet leaving the barrel and the double recoil springs along with its grip and pointability.  The combo just seems to work and creates a really accurate gun.  the slim frames and glock 36 although really close dont quite have the special magic that this model is known for.its actually pretty small, i had an xds and a glock 19, and it feels about the same maybe a little thicker but overall about the same size you will be surprised how close in size it actually is. however unlike an xds, it holds 10 +1 rounds instead of 5+1  or 7+ 1 with a giant extension hanging out the bottom.
